          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "RA-BE"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The neutron source was a mixture of 200 mC of",
                "Ra with Be, embedded 3 cm below the surface of a",
                "paraffin cylinder 15 cm high and 20 cm in diameter.",
                "Average neutron energy: 3.6 MeV (13.2 MeV max)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GEMUC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " In each case, sets of four Cd shielded",
                "detector slabs, each measuring 2.2 by 4 cm, were",
                "irradiated at a standard elevation of 35 mm above the",
                "paraffin surface in an arrangement in which they",
                "covered an area of 4.5x8 cm. For counting, the",
                "four detectors were placed on a frame which fitted",
                "around a thin-walled Geiger-Mueller counter. The",
                "counter was connected to a scale-of-eight circuit.",
                "The 44\" period of Rh and the 54' period of In were",
                "used. The routine of counting and irradiation was, of",
                "course, strictly standardized, both with regard to",
                "geometrical arrangement and to timing."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": 10.0,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Curves show that the ratios of widths",
                "and spacing have an error of less than 10 percent."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": 2.0,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The statistical error in the",
                "determination of each point was less than 2 percent."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Compiler's comment: These measurements for the 1.259",
                "eV resonance in Rh-103 (100% isotopic abundance) and",
                "1.457 eV resonance in In-115 (95.71% isotopic",
                "abundance). These resonance energies (1.259 and 1.457",
                "eV) are not mentioned in the article."
              ]
            }
          ],
